plot: Based on the comic with the same title, this series follows the adventures of police detective Sara Pezini, the bearer of the Witchblade. The Witchblade is a powerful gauntlet-like weapon with a will of its own. Existing since the dawn of time it chooses each time the right person to be merged with, and Sara is the chosen one of this generation.   Written by  Chris Makrozahopoulos
title: La espada de la hechicera
